column2: SELECT   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  gs.lgm_tot_p5# FROM Galaxy AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS gs ON gs.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE  s.class = &&&  AND gs.lgm_tot_p5# > #  AND p.u > #  AND p.g > #  AND p.r > #  AND p.i > #  AND p.z > #
